text:
Mano, welcome home.
Dinner will be ready soon.

Pii-chan, I'm back.
Thank you for being a good boy while I was out.

Just wait a moment.
I'll open it after I put away the groceries.

Today, I told Hiori-chan and
Meguru-chan about Pii-chan.
Yes, you can come out now.

So, while we were chatting,
they said they wanted to see Pii-chan again.
They'll come to play next time.

Hehe...
Yeah, I'm looking forward to it.
Well, Mom's waiting downstairs, so shall we go?
